Title: Rio Olympics: Justin Gatlin eliminated in 200m
Content: American sprinter Justin Gatlin failed to qualify for the men's 200m at the Olympics on Wednesday.Gatlin, who has served two doping bans, tied up late in his semi-final, only finishing third in 20.13
Author: AFP
